---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="About Us - Eli's Barbershop Toronto" description="Learn about Eli Chanimov and Eli's Barbershop - Toronto's premier gents barbershop." active="about">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="page-hero-inner">
      <div class="hero-slideshow" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="hero-slide" style="background-image:url('/hero-slides/slide-1.jpg')"></div>
        <div class="hero-slide" style="background-image:url('/hero-slides/slide-2.jpg')"></div>
        <div class="hero-slide" style="background-image:url('/hero-slides/slide-3.jpg')"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <div class="hero-divider"><span></span><span class="scissors">✂</span><span></span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-grid">
        <div class="about-text">
          <h2 class="section-title">About Eli's Barbershop</h2>
          <p>Founded in 2017, Eli's Barbershop is a modern space for men of all ages to get a great haircut without the fuss. Owner Eli Chanimov, a seasoned barber with years of experience, set out to create a neighborhood barbershop where everyone feels welcome. Our approach is simple—clean cuts, professional service, and a relaxed environment. We're proud to be part of the Toronto community and look forward to helping you look your best.</p>
          <div class="about-cta">
            <a href="tel:+14162242877" class="btn btn-primary">Call Us: (+1) 416 224 2877</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-outline">Contact Us</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-img">
          <img src="/gallery/b0a3f5a8-97d9-4f44-8f10-f64260a350f4.jpg" alt="Eli Chanimov at Eli's Barbershop">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="about-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Goal</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">At Eli's Barbershop, our goal goes beyond providing a quality haircut—it's about serving our neighborhood with dedication and care. We're proud to be a part of this community, and we aim to build strong, lasting relationships with every client who walks through our doors. Whether you're a regular or a first-time visitor, our focus is on creating a welcoming atmosphere and delivering a cut you'll love, every single time. We believe that great service and genuine connections are what make a barbershop truly special.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="values-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title light">Our Values</h2>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/icons/icon-comb.webp" alt="Expertise"></div>
          <h3>Expertise</h3>
          <p>Years of professional barbering experience, keeping up with trends while mastering the classics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/icons/icon-face.webp" alt="Fair Pricing"></div>
          <h3>Fair Pricing</h3>
          <p>Premium quality at honest prices. No hidden fees, no surprises - just great cuts at $25.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-icon"><img src="/icons/icon-scissors.webp" alt="Community"></div>
          <h3>Community</h3>
          <p>A welcoming space for everyone. We take pride in being part of the Toronto community.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
